{"type":null,"faqId":49387,"title":"自动旋转屏幕","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"开启重力感应\"XE \"自适应屏幕\"XE \"横屏操作\"XE \"调整屏幕朝向\"XE \"屏幕旋转\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>背景信息</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>浏览网页或图片时，旋转手机，屏幕会自动进行横竖屏切换，方便查看和操作。您还可以自行下载安装与重力感应功能相关的应用程序，比如赛车游戏，体验重力感应带来的乐趣。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>从状态栏处向下滑动，打开通知面板。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“开关”页签下，点击“自动旋转”，开启或关闭自动旋转屏幕功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5131","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294336000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":43,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}